I"s<p>Currently, I’m a (Contract) Senior User Experience Designer at <a href="https://www.santanderbank.com/">Santander Bank</a>, leading conversation design of our virtual assistant “Sandi” for the US team and UX design for the self-service value stream on web and mobile.</p>

<p>Day to day, this looks like solely supporting three development teams with UX research, UX/UI design, and conversation design for web, iOS and Android.</p>

<p>I’m part of a small, but growing design team supporting the larger digital transformation effort for the bank’s 2 million + customers in the US.  We collaborate and support each other on a weekly basis and are part of a larger global design consortium for the global bank.</p>

